In the [[Ritsuryō system]], Shōnii corresponds to the positions of [[Sadaijin|Minister of the Left]] and [[Udaijin|Minister of the Right]] under the {{ill|Kan'i sōtō system|ja|官位相当制|1=Kan'i sōtō system|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'i sōtō system|13=User:Immanuelle/Kan'i sōtō system|qq=}}. When awarded posthumously, the Rank is denoted as Zō Shōnii (贈正二位).
